      "widgets_values": [
        "# FreeFuse Flux — Model & LoRA Download Guide\n# FreeFuse Flux — 模型与LoRA下载指南\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Required Models / 所需模型 (FP8 Quantized)\n\n### 📂 text_encoders/\n• clip_l.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/clip_l.safetensors\n  EN: CLIP-L text encoder\n  中: CLIP-L 文本编码器\n\n• t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n  EN: T5-XXL text encoder (FP8 quantized)\n  中: T5-XXL 文本编码器（FP8量化）\n\n### 📂 diffusion_models/\n• flux1-dev-fp8.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux1-dev/resolve/main/flux1-dev-fp8.safetensors\n  EN: Flux.1 Dev transformer (FP8 quantized)\n  中: Flux.1 Dev 变换器模型（FP8量化）\n\n### 📂 vae/\n• ae.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Lumina_Image_2.0_Repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors\n  EN: Flux VAE autoencoder\n  中: Flux VAE 自编码器\n\n### 📂 loras/ (LoRA Files)\n• harry_potter_flux.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/lsmpp/freefuse_community_loras/resolve/main/harry_potter.safetensors\n• daiyu_lin_flux.safetensors\n  → https://huggingface.co/lsmpp/freefuse_community_loras/resolve/main/daiyu_lin.safetensors\n  EN: Download and rename to *_flux.safetensors, or change lora_name in nodes\n  中: 下载后重命名为 *_flux.safetensors，或修改节点中的 lora_name\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Directory Structure / 目录结构\n📂 ComfyUI/models/\n├─ text_encoders/\n│  ├─ clip_l.safetensors\n│  └─ t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n├─ diffusion_models/\n│  └─ flux1-dev-fp8.safetensors\n├─ vae/\n│  └─ ae.safetensors\n└─ loras/\n   ├─ harry_potter_flux.safetensors\n   └─ daiyu_lin_flux.safetensors\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Important Notes / 重要提示\n• FP8 uses ~50% less VRAM than FP16 / FP8约省50%显存\n• ~12GB VRAM for 1024×1024 / 约需12GB显存\n• Flux uses guidance embedding, NOT CFG / Flux用guidance嵌入而非CFG\n• KSampler CFG must be 1.0 for Flux / KSampler CFG必须为1.0\n• Guidance set in CLIPTextEncodeFlux (default 3.5)\n  引导值在CLIPTextEncodeFlux中设置（默认3.5）\n• For full precision, use FP16 model variants\n  如需全精度，使用FP16模型变体"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
