        "# FreeFuse Flux — Complete Parameter Guide\n# FreeFuse Flux — 完整参数指南\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## Workflow Overview / 工作流概览\nEN: FreeFuse uses a two-phase approach for multi-LoRA composition:\n  Phase 1: Collect cross-attention → generate spatial masks\n  Phase 2: Apply masks to LoRAs → full denoising generation\n中: FreeFuse 采用两阶段方法实现多LoRA合成：\n  阶段1：收集交叉注意力 → 生成空间掩码\n  阶段2：对LoRA应用掩码 → 完整去噪生成\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 1. LoRA Loader / LoRA加载器\n• adapter_name (string): Unique ID, MUST match ConceptMap\n  适配器名称：必须与ConceptMap中一致\n• strength_model (float, default=1.0): LoRA strength for transformer\n  变换器的LoRA强度\n• strength_clip (float, default=1.0): LoRA strength for text encoder\n  文本编码器的LoRA强度\n\n## 2. Concept Map / 概念映射\n• concept_text: Description text for this concept\n  MUST appear verbatim in prompt\n  概念文本：必须原样出现在提示词中\n• enable_background (bool, default=true): Background as separate concept\n  将背景作为独立概念处理\n• background_text (string): Background description (optional)\n  背景描述（可选，留空则自动检测）\n\n## 3. Token Positions / Token位置\n• filter_meaningless (bool, default=true): Remove articles/prepositions\n  过滤冠词/介词等无意义词\n• filter_single_char (bool, default=true): Remove single-char tokens\n  过滤单字符token\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 4. Phase 1 Sampler / 阶段1采样器\n\n### Core Parameters / 核心参数\n• steps (int, default=28): Total steps, MUST match Phase 2\n  总步数：须与阶段2一致\n• collect_step (int, default=5): Collect attention then early-stop\n  收集注意力后提前终止的步骤\n• cfg (float, default=1.0): Flux MUST be 1.0\n  (guidance via CLIPTextEncodeFlux)\n  Flux必须1.0（引导通过编码器设置）\n• sampler_name: euler recommended for Flux\n  Flux推荐euler\n• scheduler: simple recommended for Flux\n  Flux推荐simple\n\n### Block Selection [Flux] / Block选择\n• collect_block (int, default=18): Double-block 0-56\n  双流block索引0-56用于注意力收集\n  ★ Block 18 recommended / 推荐Block 18\n• collect_region: [SDXL only, ignored for Flux]\n  [仅SDXL，Flux忽略此参数]\n• collect_tf_index: [SDXL only, ignored for Flux]\n  [仅SDXL，Flux忽略此参数]\n\n### Similarity / 相似度计算\n• temperature (float, default=0→auto:4000):\n  Softmax temperature. Higher = sharper maps\n  Softmax温度，越高→越锐利的映射\n• top_k_ratio (float, default=0.3):\n  Ratio of top-k tokens for similarity\n  top-k token比例\n\n### LoRA Control / LoRA控制\n• disable_lora_phase1 (bool, default=true ★):\n  Disable LoRA for cleaner base-model attention\n  禁用LoRA以获取更干净的注意力 ★推荐\n\n### Mask Post-processing / 掩码后处理\n• bg_scale (float, default=0.95):\n  Background scaling. Higher = more background\n  背景缩放，越高→背景越大\n• use_morphological_cleaning (bool, default=false):\n  Clean mask boundaries with morphology\n  形态学清理掩码边界\n\n### Mask Balancing (Advanced) / 掩码平衡（高级）\n• balance_iterations (int, 15): Balanced argmax iterations\n  平衡argmax迭代次数\n• balance_lr (float, 0.01): Bias update learning rate\n  偏置更新学习率\n• gravity_weight (float, 0.00004): Centroid attraction\n  质心吸引力（空间连贯性）\n• spatial_weight (float, 0.00004): Neighbor voting\n  邻域投票（空间平滑性）\n• momentum (float, 0.2): Smoothing between iters\n  迭代间平滑动量\n• centroid_margin (float, 0.0): Clamp from borders\n  质心边界夹紧\n• border_penalty (float, 0.0): Border assignment penalty\n  边界分配惩罚\n• anisotropy (float, 1.3): H-stretch >1=wider masks\n  各向异性 >1=更宽的掩码\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 5. Mask Applicator / 掩码应用器\n\n### LoRA Masking / LoRA掩码\n• enable_token_masking (bool, true):\n  Zero LoRA at other concepts' tokens\n  在其他概念token处清零LoRA输出\n\n### Attention Bias / 注意力偏置\n• enable_attention_bias (bool, true):\n  Apply attention bias to guide cross-attention\n  启用注意力偏置引导交叉注意力\n• bias_scale (float, 5.0): Negative bias strength\n  Suppress cross-LoRA attention (5-10 typical)\n  负偏置强度（抑制跨LoRA注意力，典型值5-10）\n• positive_bias_scale (float, 1.0):\n  Enhance same-LoRA attention\n  正偏置强度（增强同LoRA注意力）\n• bidirectional (bool, true) [Flux only]:\n  Bias both img→txt and txt→img\n  双向偏置 [Flux专用]\n• use_positive_bias (bool, true):\n  Add positive bias for matched pairs\n  为匹配对添加正偏置\n• bias_blocks: Which blocks get bias\n  应用偏置的block范围\n  - all: All blocks / 所有block\n  - double_stream_only: Double blocks [Flux]\n  - single_stream_only: Single blocks [Flux]\n  - last_half_double: Last half double blocks\n  - none: Disable / 禁用\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════\n\n## 6. KSampler (Phase 2)\n• seed: Same as Phase 1 / 与阶段1相同\n• steps: MUST match Phase 1 (28) / 须一致\n• cfg: MUST be 1.0 for Flux / Flux须1.0\n• sampler/scheduler: Match Phase 1 / 与阶段1一致\n• denoise: 1.0 for full generation / 完整生成"
      ],
